column1: #Text=Our Client is a fast-growth Logistics SaaS Startup with 250 employees - seeking a Sr.
#Text=Android Developer for a full-time salary position.What you'll do...You will work on designing and developing new features and enhancements for existing and future mobile applications.
#Text=You will play an integral role in creating great user experiences.
